<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Hors ligne – Classenpoche</title>
<meta name="theme-color" content="#1e2e42">
<style>
  html,body{height:100%;margin:0;}
  body{
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;
    font-family:-apple-system,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;
    background:#f5eede;color:#152233;text-align:center;padding:2rem;
  }
  .glyph{
    width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:14px;background:#1e2e42;color:#f5eede;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:1.1rem;font-size:1.6rem;
  }
  h1{font-size:1.15rem;margin:0 0 .5rem;}
  p{font-size:.92rem;color:#4a5568;max-width:320px;line-height:1.5;margin:0 0 1.3rem;}
  button{
    appearance:none;border:0;border-radius:10px;background:#c98f3b;color:#152233;
    font-weight:600;padding:.7rem 1.3rem;font-size:.92rem;cursor:pointer;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="glyph">📡</div>
  <h1>Pas de connexion</h1>
  <p>Impossible de joindre Classenpoche pour le moment. Reconnecte-toi à internet puis réessaie.</p>
  <button onclick="location.reload()">Réessayer</button>
</body>
</html>
